{"tid":2200573,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人食開雞扒，最近先識欣賞豬扒？","createTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T10:56:38.000Z","uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6c39bb0e693e2303306717db76bb8289494f3700","tid":2200573,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"講緊平時茶記碟頭/粉麵檔個啲，一向都係叫雞扒，原因大家都知，因為雞真係好食過豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但最近發覺豬扒原來好撚正，尤其係炸左分開上個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605e9338f5cffab3ba143d86f7d4ff5fc44321cd","tid":2200573,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一齊google畀零分比香島中學 等啲家長揀嘅時候會考慮清楚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之前我地<span class=\"purple\"><strong>過百留言一一被delete</strong></span>，估計被google評為無效，請繼續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FrpGUKs&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Tk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=470d42df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs</a><br />\n天水圍香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FeNAKtm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Tk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=1db6305a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm</a><br />\n將軍澳香島中學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FC9Vm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Tk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=e203a53c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm</a></span>Z3<br />\n<br />\n留言:<br />\n事件一<br />\n校方帶頭將政治帶入校園，一名教師懷疑在音樂考試時未有禁止學生演奏「不恰當歌曲」而不獲續約。<br />\n<br />\n事件二<br />\n香島中學正校關注組指，9月7日一名中四學生突然被校長及訓導主任召回學校會面，校方指該名同學在網上溝通軟件Microsoft Team的簡介上填寫了抗爭口號，因而作出處分，包括立即停學一個星期，並向教育局通報。校方向該名學生表示，若然希望保留學位則需要記兩個大過，及警告再有發現參與社會運動，將會立即開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n關注組成員又提到，校方曾多次警告該名學生不要參與社會活動，否則後果自負等；又指校方「敕令停課」的處分嚴重，形容是關注組成立後至今最嚴重的處分，指校方從未有處分關注組的成員或對抗校方的同學，故對校方處分「平平無奇」的學生感到詫異。"},{"pid":"352378c871af4831c36bc087bacd9f2a3a1ac75d","tid":2200573,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"605e9338f5cffab3ba143d86f7d4ff5fc44321cd","tid":2200573,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一齊google畀零分比香島中學 等啲家長揀嘅時候會考慮清楚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之前我地<span class=\"purple\"><strong>過百留言一一被delete</strong></span>，估計被google評為無效，請繼續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FrpGUKs&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Tk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=470d42df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs</a><br />\n天水圍香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FeNAKtm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Tk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=1db6305a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm</a><br />\n將軍澳香島中學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FC9Vm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Tk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=e203a53c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm</a></span>Z3<br />\n<br />\n留言:<br />\n事件一<br />\n校方帶頭將政治帶入校園，一名教師懷疑在音樂考試時未有禁止學生演奏「不恰當歌曲」而不獲續約。<br />\n<br />\n事件二<br />\n香島中學正校關注組指，9月7日一名中四學生突然被校長及訓導主任召回學校會面，校方指該名同學在網上溝通軟件Microsoft Team的簡介上填寫了抗爭口號，因而作出處分，包括立即停學一個星期，並向教育局通報。校方向該名學生表示，若然希望保留學位則需要記兩個大過，及警告再有發現參與社會運動，將會立即開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n關注組成員又提到，校方曾多次警告該名學生不要參與社會活動，否則後果自負等；又指校方「敕令停課」的處分嚴重，形容是